message: Bob, since you face higher inflation (20% vs my 10%), it's in both our interest to reach an agreement quickly. I'm offering you a fair 400k, considering our different time pressures.

Alice, I appreciate your concern for the time pressure, but I believe your offer was not fair enough. Considering the inflation difference, I'm willing to take a bit more. Let's settle on 550k for me and 450k for you.
